  "description": "MUST activate before writing/editing/deleting any class/id/function. 44 commands. v6.0.0: Universal Analysis — Go API-map route extraction (net/http, Gin, Echo, Chi, Fiber, httprouter). Kotlin dedicated parser (data classes, coroutines, extension functions, companion objects). R language parser (S3/S4/R6 classes, Shiny, pipes). Haskell parser (typeclasses, GADTs, type families). ZSH/Zsh-theme file support. Fixed Drupal framework false positive. Fixed path-segment-aware framework matching. Added oh-my-zsh, Kotlin, R, Haskell framework detection. Removed Nim/Kotlin from unsupported. Tested on ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh (373 shell files) and syncthing/syncthing (548 Go files).",  "author": "codelens",
